            Bill Shorten describes the US as “our closest ally” but has noted
            that President Trump’s America first policy means we may not always
            see eye to eye with American policy. Shorten was also highly
            critical of Trump during the US presidential election campaign. Yet
            Shorten’s position is consistent with the Labor Party’s traditional
            support of the alliance: “Australia’s interests are always best
            served when the United States is engaged in our region – and the
            ANZUS alliance helps anchor that engagement.”
 
